{"tid":670310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"通菜街迷幻男驚險企跳 失足倒吊簷篷","createTime":"2018-05-19T08:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T18:58:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0d4a85767a79dc48eb80058bb3c44b6117ead5","tid":670310,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:51:34.000Z","msg":"旺角男子企跳獲救，現場通菜街194號一幢8層高唐樓，上午9時許，一名男子於高層單位情緒激動，爬出窗外簷篷危站。期間，更徒手擊碎玻璃窗，在簷篷上走來走去，驚險萬分。未幾，更爬落下一層晾衫架，一時站立一時躺下，並大聲呼叫：「你喺邊呀？」，最後更失足插穿倒掛簷篷上，險象環生，途人見狀報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，將大廈對開路段封閉，消防員張開救生氣墊戒備，並且升起雲梯，約半小時後，由兩名消防員駕起升降台將他救回，送院治理，初步懷疑他受藥物影響，正調查他尋死原因。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NVmA6dyxeqXn4evRUBo1cg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/8ece2834d12b91e11a7103d654dfd425\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNVmA6dyxeqXn4evRUBo1cg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F8ece2834d12b91e11a7103d654dfd425&h=b33d0aff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%9A%E8%8F%9C%E8%A1%97%E8%BF%B7%E5%B9%BB%E7%94%B7%E9%A9%9A%E9%9A%AA%E4%BC%81%E8%B7%B3%E3%80%80%E5%A4%B1%E8%B6%B3%E5%80%92%E5%90%8A%E7%B0%B7%E7%AF%B7-034342976.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%258F%259C%25E8%25A1%2597%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E5%25B9%25BB%25E7%2594%25B7%25E9%25A9%259A%25E9%259A%25AA%25E4%25BC%2581%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%2580%2592%25E5%2590%258A%25E7%25B0%25B7%25E7%25AF%25B7-034342976.html&d=i4R458lrHm%2FInVyxz36gUBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a45cfee2\" target=\"_blank\">https